{"tid":805920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反移民 + 環保] 德國政治洗牌 極左翼反移民環保新黨誕生","createTime":"2018-09-04T08:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T21:28:46.000Z","uid":57677,"like":20,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"faf6d280e7edd92189e2fdb32317f3ddd5298e75","tid":805920,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20180902-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%B4%97%E7%89%8C-%E6%A5%B5%E5%B7%A6%E7%BF%BC%E5%8F%8D%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E6%96%B0%E9%BB%A8%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F?ref=fb_i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F20180902-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25B4%2597%25E7%2589%258C-%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E5%25B7%25A6%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E5%258F%258D%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E8%25AA%2595%25E7%2594%259F%3Fref%3Dfb_i&d=4LxgvR7ehd5k%2F1H1t1yFw26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6c1c1db6\" target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20180902-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%B4%97%E7%89%8C-%E6%A5%B5%E5%B7%A6%E7%BF%BC%E5%8F%8D%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E6%96%B0%E9%BB%A8%E8%AA%95%E7%94%9F?ref=fb_i</a><br />\n<br />\n德國最近崛起一個新左運動&ldquo;#起來運動&rdquo;（#Aufstehen），該運動以&ldquo;反移民&rdquo;和&ldquo;保護生態&rdquo;為宗旨，將在9月4日由左翼作家和政論家沙拉-瓦根內希特（Sahra- Wagenkenecht）宣布成立。預計該黨將吸走傳統左翼社民黨的部分票倉。<br />\n<br />\n德國極右翼勢力，憑藉其反移民的訴求在民眾中間擴大勢力，德國傳統左右兩黨面對這個局面，似乎束手無策。與極右翼對應，德國政治光譜中出現極左翼空白，便由&ldquo;#起來運動&rdquo;填補。該運動除了嚴厲抨擊社會不公之外，對移民問題會採用更強硬的立場。<br />\n<br />\n起來運動目前已有4萬登記黨員，其宣稱的宗旨是：將一切左翼進步力量團結在一個計畫周圍。這個計畫就是要在歐洲頭號經濟強國中，與社會不公平作鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n這個極左翼新黨的出現，導致德國左翼政治版圖重新洗牌，挑戰傳統的左翼社民黨，吸走社民黨擁戴極左翼的選民。他們的終極目標是在德國建立一個新的左派多數，並組閣政府。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/capture_allmagne_sahra_wagenknecht.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Fcapture_allmagne_sahra_wagenknecht.png&h=f3acfdcf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"546def5ad43418e15e34125e46f7f4830b645374","tid":805920,"uid":57677,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以講解下點解環保同 本土意識是對立的？"},{"pid":"a90064a01a71677f132dd6cd78362a449064c702","tid":805920,"uid":34410,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"左已經夠on 9 仲要極左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12be131f0ffe050dc30c7c548da5ccc7976bb3e5","tid":805920,"uid":26332,"like":65,"dislike":9,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"a90064a01a71677f132dd6cd78362a449064c702","tid":805920,"uid":34410,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"左已經夠on 9 仲要極左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"人地左翼就等於香港左派？<br />\n讀多幾年書先啦垃撚圾"},{"pid":"0dec9105139e45ebc6dd3da54d61fba9126ba745","tid":805920,"uid":70429,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a90064a01a71677f132dd6cd78362a449064c702","tid":805920,"uid":34410,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:07:08.000Z","msg":"左已經夠on 9 仲要極左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 獻醜不如&hellip;"},{"pid":"20179c0352a410fc80699e0e5264c156a6ed94ae","tid":805920,"uid":141151,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"12be131f0ffe050dc30c7c548da5ccc7976bb3e5","tid":805920,"uid":26332,"like":65,"dislike":9,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"a90064a01a71677f132dd6cd78362a449064c702","tid":805920,"uid":34410,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTim